{"tid":639590,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[FIFA Pro Club] PS4 Pro Club 招人(Full time)","createTime":"2018-04-23T15:03:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T05:31:43.000Z","uid":177280,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c5077f353e129aeef4ebee8eeba495b2ebc262d8","tid":639590,"uid":177280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T15:03:55.000Z","msg":"招人位置：ST(False9型) / 任何位置<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n基本要求：<br />\n-必須係Full time、肯留低長夾，大概每晚11:30開波，多出席 <br />\n<br />\n-願意同隊友夾，配合球隊戰術 <br />\n<br />\n-有sense，現位俾波要夠快，基本俾波走位 <br />\n<br />\n-必須開mic，方便開party溝通，有禮貌(唔希望有隊友十問九唔應，開咪嘅原因係想大家可以多啲交流，理解隊友想法，令到大家磨合得更好同一齊進步)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-有追求進步嘅心態，態度正面積極<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n踢法：<br />\n- 我地隊波係踢靈活多變嘅、以地面小組滲透為主、防守反擊、兩邊斬波，咩都有啲<br />\n<br />\n- 希望隊友傳波快、俾波快、現位快、少上腳<br />\n<br />\n- 盡量少遠射，通常你選擇遠射嘅位置，總會有隊友係空檔，希望唔好錯過左入波嘅機會。當然若果差唔多完場/冇隊友可以交波時，遠射都係合理、可接受嘅。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣試腳嘅朋友，請留低聯絡方法(Telegram同psn)，講低擅長位置(主要位置、次要位置)、上線時間"},{"pid":"7d254ff85e1e1f72088cce4edf1f8a3aa7098d8e","tid":639590,"uid":63202,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T15:05:31.000Z","msg":"不了 你地好惡...."},{"pid":"d948c445ba30aafae3b4a485afa23b2b282f56e5","tid":639590,"uid":51565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T15:11:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a7756646addabc3623f78fe88cb5dc1e3887de2","tid":639590,"uid":134421,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T15:15:05.000Z","msg":"踢個proclub打咁大篇野招人<br />\n9成傻閪黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d691b461eafdd150d8f6b49fe6fbb3627a84d4f","tid":639590,"uid":51565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T15:19:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://t.me/kachun9089\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fkachun9089&d=VN1ehRobdsX%2FTtqJnUt3LC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=536991a7\